## purpose
Defines the canonical architectural role of time in CivilizationOS.

## design_intent
Time is the bounded reference axis
through which ordering,
duration,
currentness,
historicalness,
and scheduled relation
become meaningful.

## canonical_rules
- current and historical time references must remain distinguishable
- replay/reference time must not masquerade as original occurrence
- ambiguous time scope fails closed
